" Login to App Server 01
$ ssh tony@stapp01

" Check status of Apache server
# systemctl status httpd

" It shows error in the config file. 
/etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf

" Rectify the error
ServerRoot "/etc/httpd"

" Restart the service 
# systemctl status httpd

" Check from jump server if the service is working 
# curl http://stapp01:6300/

" Repeat the above steps for all App Servers. Remember each server can have error in different lines.

TIP: To go to a particular line in vi editor

: <line number>